Package: duke
Title: Makes color blind friendly visualizations with Duke's official colors
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Aidan", "Gildea", , "aidan.gildea@duke.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Mine", "\u00C7etinkaya-Rundel", email = "cetinkaya.mine@gmail.com", role = c("aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6452-2420"))
    )
Description: The aim of this package is to allow for users to create Duke 
    official visualizations in a color blind friendly way. By doing so, we can 
    ensure that visualizations within our community are accessible to everyone.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
